# ⚔️ CYBER ATTACK LIFECYCLE

---

# 🔍 1. RECONNAISSANCE

## 🎯 Tujuan
Mengumpulkan informasi target.

## 🛠 Tools

- Nmap
- Whois
- Google Dork
- Maltego

## 🧪 Aktivitas

```bash
nmap -sV 192.168.1.10
```

## 🚨 Detection

- scanning berlebihan
- request aneh
- port enumeration

## 🛡 Mitigasi

- firewall
- rate limiting
- WAF
- hide service banner

---

# 🚪 2. INITIAL ACCESS

## 🎯 Tujuan
Mendapatkan akses pertama ke sistem.

---

## 🎣 PHISHING

### 🧪 Contoh
- email palsu
- login page fake
- malicious attachment

### 🚨 Identifikasi

- domain typo
- attachment aneh
- PowerShell dari Outlook

### 🛡 Mitigasi

- MFA
- email filtering
- awareness training

---

## 🔓 BRUTE FORCE

### 🧪 Contoh

```bash
hydra -l administrator -P rockyou.txt rdp://192.168.1.5
```

### 🚨 Detection

Windows Event ID:

```text
4625 = Failed Login
```

### 🔎 Wazuh Query

```kql
event.code:4625
```

### 🛡 Mitigasi

- MFA
- account lockout
- password policy
- geo blocking

---

# 💻 3. EXECUTION

## 🎯 Tujuan
Menjalankan command atau malware.

---

## ⚡ PowerShell

### 🧪 Contoh

```powershell
powershell.exe -enc SQBFAFgA
```

### 🚨 Detection

Sysmon Event ID:

```text
1 = Process Creation
```

### 🔎 Query

```kql
powershell.exe
```

### 🛡 Mitigasi

- AppLocker
- restrict PowerShell
- Constrained Language Mode

---

## 🦠 Malware Execution

### 🚨 Identifikasi

- unsigned binary
- suspicious hash
- unexpected process

### 🛡 Mitigasi

- antivirus
- EDR
- application control

---

# 🔄 4. PERSISTENCE

## 🎯 Tujuan
Bertahan di sistem setelah reboot.

## 🧪 Contoh

- Registry Run Key
- Scheduled Task
- Startup Folder
- Windows Service

### 🚨 Detection

Sysmon Event ID:

```text
13 = Registry Modification
```

### 🛡 Mitigasi

- monitor registry
- monitor startup changes
- least privilege

---

# ⬆️ 5. PRIVILEGE ESCALATION

## 🎯 Tujuan
Menjadi Administrator/SYSTEM.

## 🚨 Identifikasi

- user tiba-tiba menjadi admin
- high integrity process

## 🛡 Mitigasi

- patching
- least privilege
- disable unnecessary privilege

---

# 🥷 6. DEFENSE EVASION

## 🎯 Tujuan
Menghindari detection.

## 🧪 Contoh

- log clearing
- obfuscation
- disable antivirus
- rename malware

## 🚨 Detection

```text
1102 = Audit Log Cleared
```

## 🛡 Mitigasi

- centralized logging
- tamper protection
- immutable logs

---

# 🔑 7. CREDENTIAL ACCESS

## 🎯 Tujuan
Mencuri credential.

## 🧪 Contoh

- Mimikatz
- LSASS dumping
- brute force

## 🚨 Detection

Sysmon Event ID:

```text
10 = Process Access
```

## 🛡 Mitigasi

- Credential Guard
- disable WDigest
- EDR

---

# 🛰 8. DISCOVERY

## 🎯 Tujuan
Memahami environment internal.

## 🧪 Command Umum

```cmd
whoami
ipconfig
hostname
net user
```

## 🚨 Detection

- enumeration command
- unusual admin activity

---

# 🌐 9. LATERAL MOVEMENT

## 🎯 Tujuan
Berpindah antar host.

## 🧪 Contoh

- SMB
- RDP
- PsExec
- WinRM

## 🚨 Detection

- remote login
- admin share access
- remote process execution

---

# 📦 10. COLLECTION

## 🎯 Tujuan
Mengumpulkan data target.

## 🚨 Detection

- suspicious ZIP
- archive besar
- screenshot activity

---

# 📡 11. COMMAND & CONTROL

## 🎯 Tujuan
Komunikasi dengan server attacker.

## 🧪 Contoh

- beaconing
- reverse shell
- HTTP callback

## 🚨 Detection

- periodic traffic
- unknown domain
- suspicious outbound connection

---

# 🚚 12. EXFILTRATION

## 🎯 Tujuan
Mengirim data keluar.

## 🚨 Detection

- upload besar
- unusual outbound traffic

## 🛡 Mitigasi

- DLP
- outbound filtering
- proxy monitoring

---

# 💥 13. IMPACT

## 🎯 Tujuan
Merusak sistem.

## 🧪 Contoh

- ransomware
- data destruction
- service stop

## 🚨 Detection

- file extension berubah
- shadow copy deleted
- encryption activity

